        "last_activity_date": 1527395329,
        "creation_date": 1527395329,
        "body": "<p>You should alias the two <code>name<\/code> columns to different things:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder( );\nsb.append( \"select s.studentId, s.name as student_name, s.lastName, \" );\nsb.append( \" b.name as book_name \" );\nsb.append( \"from student s \" );\nsb.append( \"inner join borrowedbook c on s.studentId = c.studentId \" );\nsb.append( \"inner join books b on c.bookId = b.bookId \" );\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Then access your result set using the column names <code>student_name<\/code> and <code>book_name<\/code>.<\/p>\n",
